// =============================================================================
// core/database/sqlite/native/observability/mod.vr
// =============================================================================
// Layer: 7 (consumer-facing)
// Spec: sqlite-native.md §22 (operational tooling)
//
// Metric + tracing primitives for the Database. Every counter and
// histogram is surfaced both via the public `Database.metrics()` API
// and as a row in the `dbstat` virtual table extension.
//
// Submodules:
//   * `metric`     — Counter / Gauge / Histogram primitives
//   * `registry`   — per-Connection MetricRegistry
//   * `span`       — TracingSpan record + Span protocol
//   * `exporter`   — protocol with Prometheus + OTLP-shaped impls
// =============================================================================

module core.database.sqlite.native.observability;

public module metric;
public module registry;
public module span;
public module exporter;
